  "projectType": "general",
  "projectName": "The Tub Harness",
  "projectDescription": "A macOS SwiftUI app that acts as the real-time audio processing harness for THE TUB, communicating with an external ML model server over UDP at 10 Hz to drive 11 DSP modes and log training data.",
